reviewText: Love movie, had to buy dvd after netflux discontinued it, great movie about never giving up on dreams.
I love this movie.  It's so entertaining and the lead actors are very accomplished.

I would totally recommend this movie to anyone that loves a good romantic comedy.  This movie is so sweet and is definitely a tear jerker if you're like that.  My favorite part about this movie is the music.  The plot is very entertaining and for the most part this movie is family friendly.
